---
title: Quick Beef-Pork Ragu & Carrot Noodles with Bacon, Parmesan & Radish Salad
description: Everyone lovse a beef and pork ragu with their preferred kind of pasta, but hear us out on this because carrot noodles
may be the next spaghetti. Their vibrant colour warms the plate and they soak up every bit of the ragu so you can
grab a big mouthful. Trust us, this is one you don’t want to miss.
